00:01:32,259 --> 00:01:35,518
A Life, the living monitor.

9
00:01:36,096 --> 00:01:37,785
Impressed?

10
00:01:39,967 --> 00:01:41,651
Yeah, I am.

11
00:01:42,069 --> 00:01:46,131
Would you put one of those in a box for me?

12
