Sometimes it's easier if you work backwards.

33
00:05:25,993 --> 00:05:27,580
Cheers.

34
00:05:41,608 --> 00:05:44,264
You won't remember me, will you?

35
00:05:45,079 --> 00:05:46,631
No.

36
00:05:47,915 --> 00:05:49,934
That's too bad.

37
00:06:21,415 --> 00:06:23,434
Marker reached.

38
00:06:39,933 --> 00:06:41,292
OK.

39
